            <title><![CDATA[【[干饭人]#长时间冷冻的馒头还能吃吗#】深色馒头指的是杂粮馒头，一般由荞麦或莜麦制作而成，其膳食纤维大约是精制米面的25倍，#深色馒头更有助控制血糖#。但长...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[干饭人]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/cb/2022_Foodie_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%95%BF%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%86%B7%E5%86%BB%E7%9A%84%E9%A6%92%E5%A4%B4%E8%BF%98%E8%83%BD%E5%90%83%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%95%BF%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%86%B7%E5%86%BB%E7%9A%84%E9%A6%92%E5%A4%B4%E8%BF%98%E8%83%BD%E5%90%83%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#长时间冷冻的馒头还能吃吗#</span></a>】深色馒头指的是杂粮馒头，一般由荞麦或莜麦制作而成，其膳食纤维大约是精制米面的25倍，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B7%B1%E8%89%B2%E9%A6%92%E5%A4%B4%E6%9B%B4%E6%9C%89%E5%8A%A9%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E8%A1%80%E7%B3%96%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%B7%B1%E8%89%B2%E9%A6%92%E5%A4%B4%E6%9B%B4%E6%9C%89%E5%8A%A9%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E8%A1%80%E7%B3%96%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#深色馒头更有助控制血糖#</span></a>。但长期食用精制米面，容易造成维生素和矿物质摄入不足，甚至导致维生素缺乏。馒头冷冻时间太长会导致滋生“一类致癌物”吗？👇🏻（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6YjrUj8" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
